WEBVTT

00:00.201 --> 00:01.236
Previously on "Heartland":

00:01.639 --> 00:03.072
What are you up to
with Spartan?

00:03.140 --> 00:04.573
I don't really know
what it is myself yet,

00:04.641 --> 00:06.575
I'm just trying
something out.

00:06.643 --> 00:07.876
Very mysterious.

00:07.943 --> 00:09.211
Did you just jump ship,

00:09.279 --> 00:10.479
or do you always come to the bar
in a swimsuit?

00:10.547 --> 00:12.981
If this were 1998,
it would make sense.

00:13.049 --> 00:14.783
How old are you,
anyway?

00:14.850 --> 00:16.318
Old enough to know

00:16.386 --> 00:17.852
I should not be wasting my time
with guys like you!

00:17.920 --> 00:18.853
Whoa! Oof!

00:18.921 --> 00:20.020
Caleb?

00:20.088 --> 00:21.355
Jack? Come here, buddy!

00:21.423 --> 00:23.891
I want you to meet
a real good friend of mine.

00:26.161 --> 00:27.228
Surf's up!

00:29.130 --> 00:30.531
<i>Hey cow!</i>

00:32.267 --> 00:33.801
Hooo!

00:35.136 --> 00:36.436
<i>Come on, cow!</i>

00:38.472 --> 00:40.674
Hey, let's call it a day, huh?

00:40.741 --> 00:41.741
What?

00:41.809 --> 00:43.343
Let's call it a day!

00:43.411 --> 00:45.178
Well, let's finish
the job first.

00:45.246 --> 00:46.746
Okay, fine.
But I'm telling you,

00:46.814 --> 00:49.416
I'm sore and I'm tired,
and my shoulder is killin' me!

00:49.483 --> 00:50.684
Don't make me cry!

00:51.784 --> 00:53.252
Two days in the saddle...

00:53.320 --> 00:55.187
Is not doing much for my back,
I'll tell you that.

00:55.255 --> 00:57.690
We should've hired some guys
to help us move these cows.

00:57.757 --> 00:58.824
Oh, quit complaining!

00:58.891 --> 01:00.826
You sound like
an old geezer.

01:00.893 --> 01:02.861
Ha-ha! Geezer!

01:02.929 --> 01:04.096
I'm not the one

01:04.163 --> 01:05.931
with the big birthday coming up,
Jack.

01:05.998 --> 01:09.133
If you're gonna whine about
every little ache and pain,

01:09.201 --> 01:11.336
God help us all
when you are my age!

01:11.403 --> 01:12.537
Oh please!

01:12.605 --> 01:13.938
You won't be around
to see that.

01:14.005 --> 01:16.040
You'll be taking a dirt nap
by then.

01:16.108 --> 01:18.476
Well, thankfully,
that's true.

01:18.544 --> 01:21.312
I won't be around to hear
all your moaning and groaning!

